    </media>
    <caption><emphasis effect="bold">IR spectra of (a) hexane, (b) 1-hexene, and (c) 1-hexyne.</emphasis> Spectra like these are easily obtained from sub-milligram amounts of material in a few minutes using commercially available instruments.</caption>
